title: Preseason Rookie Power Rankings
description:
Jason Goff and Austin Gayle get together to share their performance evaluations for some of the exciting new talent around the league after the first slate of NFL preseason action and discuss how they are able to develop under the new CBA agreement.
Hosts: Jason Goff and Austin Gayle
Production Supervision: Arjuna Ramgopal
Production Assistance: Chris Sutton
